OL,3,CLifeguards acquitted over swimmer's
OL,4,Cdeath
OL,6,FThree lifeguards have been found not
OL,7,Fguilty of neglecting their duty of
OL,8,Fcare following the death of a swimmer
OL,9,Fin Armagh nearly seven years ago.
OL,11,FChristopher Rogers was 20-years-old
OL,12,Fwhen he died after training in the
OL,13,Fswimming pool at Orchard Leisure
OL,14,FCentre in April 2017.
OL,16,FOn trial were three lifeguards at
OL,17,FNewry Crown Court, who were employees
OL,18,Fat Orchard Leisure Centre in Armagh in
OL,19,F2017.
