OL,3,CLifeguards acquitted over swimmer's
OL,4,Cdeath
OL,6,FThey were 35-year-old Cathal Forrest-
OL,7,FMcVeigh of Dunamony Road in Dungannon,
OL,8,F26-year-old James Monaghan of Folly
OL,9,FLane and William Holden, also 26 and
OL,10,Fof Unshinagh Lane, both in Armagh.
OL,12,FAfter deliberating for an hour and 50
OL,13,Fminutes, the jury returned with a
OL,14,Funanimous verdict.
OL,16,FThe court previously heard that
OL,17,FChristopher Rogers who was described
OL,18,Fas a "very, very strong swimmer",
OL,19,Fsuffered an hypoxic blackout towards
OL,20,Fthe middle of the pool.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
