OL,6,FAfter swimming two and a half lengths,
OL,7,Fhe came to the surface before
OL,8,Fdescending to the bottom of the pool
OL,9,Fafter becoming unconscious.
OL,11,FCPR was delivered by the side of the
OL,12,Fpool. He was rushed to hospital where
OL,13,Fhe died in the early hours of the next
OL,14,Fmorning.
OL,16,FBefore sending the jury to deliberate,
OL,17,Fthe judge said this had been a
OL,18,F"shattering emotional trial for
OL,19,Feveryone involved."
