OL,6,FWhen the verdict was delivered,
OL,7,FWilliam Holden wiped away tears.
OL,9,FChanges were made by the leisure
OL,10,Fcentre in how long someone could swim
OL,11,Funderwater for in the aftermath of
OL,12,FChristopher Rogers death.
